snippet.title: Nightmare Kart Expansion DLC: The Old Karts
snippet.description:
Nightmare Kart: The Old Karts is a free expansion DLC that will add new content to the game that is coming soon!

💉 New mini campaign!
🏎️ New racers & karts!
🗺️ New tracks!
💥 New power ups & game modes!

Press kit here: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1EOm5yczcOFrTJUjC9MCIqGlkcFDD1xdq?usp=drive_link
Support this game on patreon! https://patreon.com/lwmedia
Keep up to date on development via bluesky: https://b0tster.yeag.gay
Music by @TheNobleDemon: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WWkwxyu9fHU
VO By Tom Schalk: https://bsky.app/profile/tomschalk.bsky.social
